Press conference with Chelsea Head Coach Thomas Tuchel following their Champions League exit at the hands of Real Madrid. According to Tuchel, his side deserved better but they were just unlucky as their opponents capitalized on two mistakes his side made. He said Madrid players displayed individual brilliance, quality conversion and offensive conversion every time they won the ball from his side. "We deserved to go through after this performance and after this ,match today but it was not to be, as you know you need luck," Tuchel said after the match.